translation[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,Ke kaloku benzele umzekeliso (wabantu) besixeko (esithile) ekwafika abaThunywa kuso
  36,14,"Sathi Sisakuthumela ababini kubo basuka babaphika, Saza Sabomeleza ngowesithathu, bathi: “Inene thina singabathunywa kuni.”"
  36,15,"Bathi bona: “Aninto yimbi nina ngaphandle kokuba ngabantu abafana nathi, kunjalo nje uSozinceba Akananto Ayityhilileyo (kuni) koko nina ningamaxoki.”"
  36,16,"Bathi bona: “INkosi yethu Iyazi okokuba singabaThunywa kuni"
  36,17,Yaye thina asinaxanduva lumbi ngaphandle kokuvakalisa uMyalezo ngokucacileyo.”
  36,18,"Bathi bona: “Inene thina sinicingela ukuba ningumhlola ombi. Ukuba aniyeki ke inene siya kunixuluba ngamatye, kwaye inene niya kufunyanwa sisohlwayo esibuhlungu esivela kuthi.”"
  36,19,"Bathi bona (abathunywa): “Umhlola ombi ukuni buqu. Ingaba (nikutsho oku) kuba nikhunjuzwa (ngoAllâh) kusini na?” Nakanye nina ningabenzi bobubi.”"
  36,20,"Ke kaloku kweza indoda ibaleka, ivela kwicala elikude lesixeko. Yathi: “Hini na bantu bakuthi landelani abaThunywa"
  36,21,Landelani abo banganibizi ntlawulo babe bengabakhokelelekileyo
  36,22,Ndiya kuthini na ukungamnquli loWo Wandidalayo ekunguYe eniza kubuyiselwa kuYe
  36,23,"Ndingathabatha (thixo) bambi na ngaphandle kwaKhe (lo gama) xa uSozinceba Enokuthi Athande ukuba ndihlelwe bububi intethelelo yabo (thixo benu bobuxoki) ingandincedi nto konke konke, bengekhe bandisindise nokundisindisa"
  36,24,Inene bendingaba sekulahlekeni okucacileyo
  36,25,"Inene mna ndikholiwe eNkosini yenu, ngoko ke ndiphulaphuleni.”"
  36,26,"Kwathiwa (kuye:) “Ngena ePaladesi.” Wathi yena: “Akwaba abantu bakuthi babesazi"
  36,27,"Okokuba Indixolele kangakanani na iNkosi yam, Yandibeka kunye nabahloniphekileyo.”"